author: gtully
msg: further resolution to https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2980, concurrent producers was still problematic as the store needed to be traversed multiple times, requiring ack locations per priority. Resolution to https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2551 fell out of decreasing the cleanup interval in some of the tests, cleanup needs an exclusive lock so it won't cause contention
